{"tid":1203232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非非既你唔該轉場去美國領事館","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T07:02:34.000Z","uid":42434,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9587d090ace776d585209d375af496bbb3d11f52","tid":1203232,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"到呢一步其實大家都唔會希望啲咩<br />\n唯一希望既係要美國制裁呢班賤種<br />\n等美國取消香港政策法<br />\n等香港經濟收皮 <br />\n班賤人都唔好過<br />\n再有可能立埋香港人權法<br />\n凍結佢地係美國既資產<br />\n唔準入境美國<br />\n希望歐洲可以跟隨<br />\n<br />\n係美國領事館門口坐<br />\n一黎美國一定睇住，因為自己領事館門口<br />\n二黎有其他國家關注<br />\n三黎領事館門口班黑警唔敢太誇張"},{"pid":"0f0dbe2e3f17c11d3b77a9a86f66ebd8dcf0929c","tid":1203232,"uid":39855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"60a22314f89c7e6f2feb353633fef13a27f009a7","tid":1203232,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b67dd60f0989b97af68b3c1e0d14d97b2248196","tid":1203232,"uid":22155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c46b506f15d8725bd143ed35c21a811cc499d1e1","tid":1203232,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"多d人 無咁易比人包？"},{"pid":"7dba766249cae70bdb5c0a0ef9953dd2d612a57c","tid":1203232,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b0396c82d5c2df8fc864e4ffba90773231c5882","tid":1203232,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"25a67d918399fcff0b2a2ab227e0366a39b39b73","tid":1203232,"uid":43664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e892a31b06767d3c62b45af6b8e2ad39a15dea7e","tid":1203232,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae2d